name: James Fischer
description: Hi my name is Selina and I’m single and never married . I’m 36years old . I was born and raised in Cleveland , Ohio but currently living at college park , Georgia . I’m simple and a serious lady here . I’m too old for games and jokes . I’m new here looking for someone honest and loving to meet and see where it goes . I consider my self as loving , serious , honest and faithful lady . I don’t take relationships for granted . I only want to meet someone real and simple to grow old with . I came from a simple and happy family and I can say that I am so blessed to have them in my life. I’m a woman who never wastes time And play games .
